data.text: Isabel Cooixet is one of the most prestigious Spanish cinema directors of our time. She has been awarded several times for movies like The secret life of words, My life without me or Nobody wants the night. This cinema cycle showcases the ultimate movies of the director, approaching her cinema to the newyorkers.
